---
import PageShell from '../../components/PageShell.astro';
import CTABox from '../../components/CTABox.astro';
import ComparisonTable from '../../components/ComparisonTable.astro';

const tocItems = [
  { id: 'overview', text: 'Overview', level: 2 },
  { id: 'coverage-comparison', text: 'Coverage Comparison', level: 2 },
  { id: 'pricing', text: 'Pricing', level: 2 },
  { id: 'network-and-claims', text: 'Network and Claims', level: 2 },
  { id: 'who-should-choose', text: 'Who Should Choose Which', level: 2 },
  { id: 'verdict', text: 'Our Verdict', level: 2 },
];

const relatedLinks = [
  { title: 'AXA Global Review', href: '/providers/axa-global' },
  { title: 'BUPA Global Review', href: '/providers/bupa-global' },
  { title: 'Best Expat Insurance', href: '/best/expat-health-insurance' },
  { title: 'France Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/france/insurance' },
  { title: 'UK Insurance Guide', href: '/countries/uk/insurance' },
];

const coverageColumns = [
  { key: 'feature', header: 'Feature' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
];

const coverageRows = [
  { feature: 'Inpatient Care', axa: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Outpatient Care', axa: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Mental Health', axa: 'Good', bupa: 'Excellent' },
  { feature: 'Maternity', axa: 'Optional', bupa: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Dental', axa: 'Optional', bupa: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Vision', axa: 'Optional', bupa: 'Optional' },
  { feature: 'Pre-Existing Conditions', axa: 'Moratorium', bupa: 'Full medical underwriting' },
  { feature: 'Medical Evacuation', axa: true, bupa: true },
  { feature: 'Annual Maximum', axa: '€1M-Unlimited', bupa: '$2M-Unlimited' },
  { feature: 'Regulatory Framework', axa: 'EU-regulated', bupa: 'UK-regulated' },
];

const pricingColumns = [
  { key: 'profile', header: 'Profile' },
  { key: 'axa', header: 'AXA Global' },
  { key: 'bupa', header: 'BUPA Global' },
];

const pricingRows = [
  { profile: 'Single, Age 30', axa: '€110-150/mo', bupa: '$200-280/mo' },
  { profile: 'Single, Age 45', axa: '€180-240/mo', bupa: '$350-450/mo' },
  { profile: 'Couple, Age 35', axa: '€220-300/mo', bupa: '$400-560/mo' },
  { profile: 'Family of 4', axa: '€380-520/mo', bupa: '$700-1,000/mo' },
];
---

<PageShell
  title="AXA Global vs BUPA Global"
  description="Compare AXA Global and BUPA Global side by side. Two premium European insurers—see which offers better value for your needs."
  headline="AXA Global vs BUPA Global: Premium European Insurers Compared"
  subheadline="Both are top-tier options with strong European roots. Here's how to choose between them."
  heroBackgroundImage="/images/compare/axa-vs-bupa-hero-bg.png"
  tocItems={tocItems}
  relatedLinks={relatedLinks}
  ctaButtonText="Get Quotes from Both"
  ctaButtonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
>
  <h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>
  <p>
    AXA Global and BUPA Global are both premium international health insurers with strong European heritage. AXA is French (EU-regulated), while BUPA is British (UK-regulated). Both offer comprehensive coverage, but at different price points and with different strengths.
  </p>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">AXA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>EU-regulated (French insurer)</li>
        <li>More competitive pricing</li>
        <li>Strong European networks</li>
        <li>Good value for comprehensive coverage</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">BUPA Global</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>UK-regulated (British insurer)</li>
        <li>Premium pricing, premium service</li>
        <li>Excellent mental health coverage</li>
        <li>Strong pre-existing condition options</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <CTABox
    title="Compare Both Providers"
    description="Get quotes from AXA Global and BUPA Global for your situation."
    buttonText="Get Free Quotes"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <h2 id="coverage-comparison">Coverage Comparison</h2>
  <p>
    Both insurers offer comprehensive coverage. The differences are in the details—particularly mental health coverage and how they handle pre-existing conditions.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={coverageColumns} rows={coverageRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Key differences:</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Mental health:</strong> BUPA Global has some of the best mental health coverage in the industry. AXA's is good but not as comprehensive</li>
    <li><strong>Pre-existing conditions:</strong> BUPA offers full medical underwriting, which can mean better coverage if you qualify. AXA uses moratorium underwriting (conditions excluded until claim-free period passes)</li>
    <li><strong>Regulation:</strong> AXA's EU regulation provides strong consumer protections. BUPA's UK regulation is also robust but different</li>
  </ul>

  <h2 id="pricing">Pricing</h2>
  <p>
    AXA Global is significantly more affordable than BUPA Global—often 30-40% less for similar coverage levels.
  </p>

  <div class="my-8 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
    <ComparisonTable columns={pricingColumns} rows={pricingRows} />
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Notes on pricing:</strong>
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>BUPA's premium pricing reflects their premium service and extensive benefits</li>
    <li>AXA offers similar core coverage at a lower price point</li>
    <li>Both offer high-deductible options to reduce premiums</li>
    <li>The gap widens with age—BUPA's premiums increase more steeply</li>
  </ul>

  <CTABox
    title="Get Your Actual Price"
    description="Prices vary significantly by age and coverage choices."
    buttonText="Get a Quote"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
  />

  <h2 id="network-and-claims">Network and Claims</h2>

  <h3>Provider Networks</h3>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> has extensive direct-billing relationships worldwide, with particularly strong networks in the UK, Europe, and Asia.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>AXA Global</strong> has excellent European coverage and growing networks elsewhere. Direct billing is available at major hospitals but may be less extensive than BUPA's.
  </p>

  <h3>Claims Process</h3>
  <p>
    Both offer online claims submission and mobile apps. BUPA's claims process is often praised as one of the smoothest in the industry. AXA's is reliable but may take slightly longer.
  </p>

  <h3>Customer Service</h3>
  <p>
    BUPA Global is known for exceptional customer service with dedicated case managers. AXA provides solid 24/7 support but BUPA's service is generally rated higher.
  </p>

  <h2 id="who-should-choose">Who Should Choose Which</h2>

  <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
    <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose AXA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Value for money is important</li>
        <li>You want EU regulatory protections</li>
        <li>You're primarily based in Europe</li>
        <li>You don't have complex pre-existing conditions</li>
        <li>You want comprehensive coverage without premium pricing</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-200 rounded-lg p-6">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-3">Choose BUPA Global If:</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600">
        <li>Mental health coverage is a priority</li>
        <li>You have pre-existing conditions to declare</li>
        <li>You want premium service and support</li>
        <li>Budget is less of a concern</li>
        <li>You value the most extensive provider network</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="verdict">Our Verdict</h2>
  <p>
    Both AXA Global and BUPA Global are excellent choices—this is a comparison between two premium options, not good vs bad.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>AXA Global</strong> offers the better value proposition for most people. You get comprehensive coverage, EU regulatory protections, and solid service at a significantly lower price point.
  </p>
  <p>
    <strong>BUPA Global</strong> is worth the premium if mental health coverage is important to you, if you have pre-existing conditions that need full underwriting, or if you simply want the best service and most extensive network regardless of cost.
  </p>
  <p>
    Get quotes from both to see the actual price difference for your situation—it might be larger or smaller than the estimates above.
  </p>

  <CTABox
    title="Ready to Decide?"
    description="Compare quotes from both providers based on your specific needs."
    buttonText="Compare Plans Now"
    buttonHref="/best/expat-health-insurance"
    variant="highlight"
  />

  <div class="bg-neutral-50 border border-neutral-200 rounded-lg p-6 mt-8">
    <p class="text-sm text-neutral-600">
      <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> This comparison is for informational purposes only. Prices, coverage, and plan details change. We are not insurance brokers. Verify all information with the providers before purchasing.
    </p>
  </div>
</PageShell>
